# ::tok Mike Johnson , Trump - backed conservative , elected House Republican Chairman—powerful , loyal , but concerning for the nation 's future .
(p / person~0
    :name (n / name~0
        :op1 "Mike"~0
        :op2 "Johnson"~1)
    :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91~11
        :ARG1 (g / government-organization~9
            :name (n3 / name~9
                :op1 "House"~9)
            :mod (p3 / political-party~10
                :name (n4 / name~10
                    :op1 "Republican"~10)))
        :ARG2 (m / member~11))
    :ARG1-of (b / back-01~5
        :ARG0 (p2 / person~3
            :name (n2 / name~3
                :op1 "Trump"~3)))
    :ARG1-of (e / elect-01~8
        :ARG2 g)
    :ARG1-of (l / loyal-01~13
        :ARG1-of (c3 / contrast-01~15
            :ARG2 (c / concern-01~16
                :ARG0 p
                :ARG1 (f / future~21
                    :poss (n5 / nation~19)))))
    :mod (c2 / conservative~6)
    :rel n
    :rel "Mike"~0
    :rel "Johnson"~1
    :rel n2
    :rel "Trump"~3
    :rel p2
    :rel b
    :rel c2
    :rel e
    :rel n3
    :rel "House"~9
    :rel p3
    :rel n4
    :rel "Republican"~10
    :rel h
    :rel m
    :rel l
    :rel c3
    :rel c
    :rel n5
    :rel f)
